message:
I created an automatic image generation script for character chats.
The idea was to more or less slap that into the script box and have image generation in any chat.
Here is an example with the base Yume character:
https://perchance.org/ai-character-chat?data=Yume~2797c6a5f95b791e695c35fc098bd444.gz

Feel free to do whatever you want with it.
